I loved this!!!!!!!! It was perfect! I actually got to watch all of them because they never aired on tv...warning: it can be explicit at times

The third season of Mujeres Asesinas is one of the best by far. I ordered it because Univison didn't finish showing it on their channel. I think they hava a reason why they did that. But back to Mujeres Asesinas 3 will recommend it the other half of the season that they didn't show is way much better. They are saving the best for last. The stories from this season is way much better and go into more details. The stories will keep you on the edge of your seat and will make you to rewatch it!!!! Will recommend people to buy it if they cant wait for them to reshow it on Univison. Buy the DVD set worth the money!!!
